From f77f52d89b558a526a6e6cd32647b64773518522 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: BodyLog Dev <dev@bodylog.app>
Date: Tue, 26 May 2026 22:19:21 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: auto-import patient records + sidebar toggle fix
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- server.js: POST /api/patients/:id/self-record now auto-imports to
  p.records immediately (source:'patient', imported:true).
  No manual import step needed anymore.
- admin.html: SSE handler refreshes detail/records/chart on new-record.
  showAutoImportBanner() replaces old import button workflow.
  Polling fallback updated to detect new arrivals by count.
  '記録に取り込む' button replaced with '自動で記録に反映済み' label.
- admin.html: sidebar toggleSidebar/closeSidebar + overlay already applied.
---
 admin.html | 87 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---------------
 server.js  | 34 +++++++++++++++++++--
 2 files changed, 95 insertions(+), 26 deletions(-)

